summary: An Ordinance vacating a portion of Northlake Avenue abutting upon lots 1, 2, 3 and 4, in block 53, and lots 1 and 2, in block 52, Kilbourne's Supplemental Plat of Lake Union Addition, and all of Eugene Street lying between said lot 4, block 53, and said lot 1, block 52, and a triangular tract of land lying between said lot 1, block 53, and said lot 1, block 38, and being at the junction of Kilbourne Street and Sunnyside Avenue.
